{{!-- Site-wide cover-image caption.
     Renders Ghost's feature_image_caption value (set per-post in the
     Ghost editor under "Image > Caption") as a small white label tucked
     into the bottom-left corner of the hero image. Styled to match the
     hardcoded photo credit on the About page.

     Wrap in a div (not <p>) because Ghost's caption value already comes
     back as block-level HTML in some cases — nesting <p> inside <p> is
     invalid and silently breaks layout in Safari. The {{{triple-stash}}}
     is required so Ghost-authored HTML (links, italics) renders.

     The parent .archive-entry-image must be position: relative for the
     absolute positioning in style.css to anchor correctly. Every reader
     using this partial already satisfies that. --}}

{{#if feature_image_caption}}
  <div class="feature-image-caption">{{{feature_image_caption}}}</div>
{{/if}}
